          "id": "welcome",
          "kind": "builtin:markdown",
          "title": "Welcome",
          "grid": { "x": 0, "y": 0, "w": 12, "h": 5 },
          "collapsed": false,
          "hidden": false,
          "props": {
            "markdown": "# Welcome to Agent HQ\n\nThis whole dashboard is one JSON document — **any AI can build it, any human can edit it.**\n\n- Click **🤖 simulate agent** above to watch an agent compose a new view live.\n- Drag widgets, resize them, or hit *undo* — you're editing the same document the agent uses.\n- Approve (or reject) any agent-authored widget before it ever runs — sandboxed, by construction.\n\nAsk something below to see the action-form pattern in action."
          }
        },
        {
          "id": "ask-agent",
          "kind": "builtin:action-form",
          "title": "Ask the Agent",
          "grid": { "x": 0, "y": 5, "w": 6, "h": 6 },
          "collapsed": false,
          "hidden": false,
          "props": {
            "template": "Draft a {tone} summary about {topic}.",
            "fields": [
              { "name": "topic", "label": "Topic", "type": "text", "maxLength": 80 },
              {
                "name": "tone",
                "label": "Tone",
                "type": "select",
                "options": ["concise", "friendly", "formal"]
              }
            ],
            "buttonLabel": "Ask the agent"
          }
        }
      ]
